snippet.title: C64 Longplay - Kokotoni Wilf
snippet.description:
Jet Set Willy with wings. Dated-looking but fun platformer programmed by Neil A. Bate and released in 1984 by Elite.

REVIEW: https://archive.org/details/commodore-user-magazine-16/page/n61/mode/2up
